      <title>即将离任的 SEC 执法主管 Grewal 将加入 Milbank 律师事务所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/departing-sec-enforcement-chief-grewal-to-join-milbank-law-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国证券交易委员会最高执法官员古尔比尔·格雷瓦尔（Gurbir Grewal）将于本月晚些时候离开该监管机构，并加入米尔班克（Milbank）律师事务所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/departing-sec-enforcement-chief-grewal-to-join-milbank-law-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 21:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
