      <title>野村证券：鲍威尔的巨大影响力预示着美联储降息幅度将有所缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/powell-s-outsized-influence-signals-smaller-fed-cut-nomura-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村证券国际的 Aichi Amemiya 表示，美联储很可能会在 11 月和 12 月的政策会议上将降息幅度降至 25 个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/powell-s-outsized-influence-signals-smaller-fed-cut-nomura-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 21:03:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
